            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%99%A8%E7%BB%83%E6%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%A9%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%99%A8%E7%BB%83%E6%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%A9%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#晨练更有助睡眠#</span></a> 晨练会影响到晚上的睡眠？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[睡]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuijiao-4cb62c7d81.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A4%9C%E8%B7%91%E5%92%8C%E6%99%A8%E8%B7%91%E5%93%AA%E4%B8%AA%E6%9B%B4%E8%83%BD%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A4%9C%E8%B7%91%E5%92%8C%E6%99%A8%E8%B7%91%E5%93%AA%E4%B8%AA%E6%9B%B4%E8%83%BD%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#夜跑和晨跑哪个更能改善睡眠#</span></a>？专家提示，晨练更有助睡眠，运动会促进人体产生腺苷，有助于产生困意，能睡得更好。夜跑虽然也会产生腺苷，但同时会升高身体的核心体温，人会更精神。另外，临睡前的两个小时之内，不要做剧烈的运动。 <a href="http://t.cn/A6pvY5Mc" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
